    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You install an AI into a vehicle that can control the vehicle in place of an actual pilot. During the spell&rsquo;s duration, you can engage or disengage the autopilot AI as a swift action. You can input a destination into the autopilot AI as a move action, and the autopilot AI attempts to reach that location if doing so is possible.</p>\n<p>The vehicle is considered controlled when the autopilot AI is engaged. The autopilot AI&rsquo;s actions are dictated by the GM, and the autopilot AI can take any of the actions to pilot a vehicle that an actual pilot can. The autopilot AI has a Piloting modifier of +14.</p>"
